svadlamuri@LAPTOP-1BR3SJJG:~/file1$ telnet localhost 2> errorfile
Trying 127.0.0.1...

note: error goes to
svadlamuri@LAPTOP-1BR3SJJG:~/file1$ cat errorfile
telnet: Unable to connect to remote host: Connection refused


